    "Small but noticeable app-wide improvements. The app will still feel instantly familiar, just with a more refined and timeless look." : {
      "localizations" : {
        "ar" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "تحسينات صغيرة ولكنها ملحوظة على مستوى التطبيق. سيظل التطبيق مألوفًا على الفور، فقط بمظهر أكثر دقة وخالدًا."
          }
        },
        "de" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Kleine, aber spürbare App-weite Verbesserungen."
          }
        },
        "en" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Small but noticeable app-wide improvements. The app will still feel instantly familiar, just with a more refined and timeless look."
          }
        },
        "es" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Pequeñas pero notables mejoras en toda la app. La app seguirá sintiéndose familiar al instante, solo que con un aspecto más refinado y atemporal."
          }
        },
        "fr" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "De petites améliorations mais bien perceptibles dans toute l’app. L’application restera immédiatement familière, avec simplement une apparence plus raffinée et intemporelle."
          }
        },
        "pt-BR" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Melhorias pequenas, mas perceptíveis em todo o aplicativo. O aplicativo ainda parecerá instantaneamente familiar, apenas com uma aparência mais refinada e atemporal."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "小但引人注目的应用程序范围内的改进。该应用程序仍然会让人立即感到熟悉，只是外观更加精致和永恒。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Some planned expenses from this preset have recorded spending. Review them below if you want to delete any." : {
      "localizations" : {
